item.title: BSDCan 2018
item.description: BSDCan 2018 (https://www.bsdcan.org/2018/), University of Ottawa, Ottawa, Canada 2018 年 06 月 06 - 09 日. A four day BSD conference held in Ottawa, Canada. BSDCan hosts talks and tutorials on a range of topics based around the BSD family of operating systems.
